From 1554a69f38e3e090fbe61fba8d388f465ef1a47e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Nazir Galimov <nazir.galimov@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 15 Feb 2026 22:38:56 +0500
Subject: [PATCH] feat(image editor): add canvas rotation support
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Add a rotation field to the SpaceImage struct to store canvas rotation in radians.
Introduce three new operators: rotate 90° clockwise, rotate 90° counter-clockwise,
and reset rotation. Add UI menu items in the View menu and default keymaps (comma
and period keys). Expose the rotation property to RNA for animation and drivers.
Update the image engine's transformation matrix to apply the visual rotation,
ensuring pan and zoom work correctly in the rotated view. The rotation is
normalized to the range [-π, π].
